highlights.text: “2 Phut Hon Funk” by Hexora, Artox, and Alert is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #90.
Tùng has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “ĐẶT TRÁI TIM LÊN BÀN” is the highest at #4.
“blue” by yung kai has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 196 days straight.
“Tình Về Nơi Đâu” by Thanh Bùi and Tata Young is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 19 spots at #59.
